com.coveros.selenified.selenium

Class LocatorAction

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.coveros.selenified.selenium.LocatorAction

  • public class LocatorAction
extends Object
    An extension of the custom selenium wrapper class, focusing on checks involving elements. This should never be called directly from any test steps, but instead supports the Action class
    Version:
    2.0.1
    Author:
    Max Saperstone
